Introduction

Dawon is a South Korean singer and actor under FNC Entertainment. As a trainee, he appeared in AOA Cream's "I'm Jelly Baby" music video. Dawon is best known for his variety show skills, even becoming a regular cast in SBS' "Game Show". He also starred in the drama "Doom at Your Service" in 2021.

He debuted as the lead vocalist of SF9 on October 5, 2016 with the group's first single album "Feeling Sensation".

On May 20, 2024 FNC took to SF9's fan cafe to post that Dawon will be enlisting as an active duty soldier on July 1st, 2024.
